            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37846",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=purpleankh",
                        "name": "purpleankh",
                        "displayName": "purple ankh",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "With reference to the final note about the Submit button, this has been reported as [ZF-8764|http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/browse\/ZF-8764].",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=purpleankh",
                        "name": "purpleankh",
                        "displayName": "purple ankh",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-20T05:06:40.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-20T05:06:40.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/38512",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ikr",
                        "name": "ikr",
                        "displayName": "Ivan Krechetov",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "For us this issue is very important, as far as we have an interactive translation mode. It allows to change the site texts right where you see them in the graphical user interface. To do this we have to append stuff to translated strings on the runtime. Like this:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n<?php\r\n\r\nset_include_path(\r\n    implode(\r\n        PATH_SEPARATOR,\r\n        array(dirname(__FILE__) . '\/library', get_include_path())\r\n    )\r\n);\r\n\r\nrequire_once 'Zend\/Loader\/Autoloader.php';\r\n\r\nZend_Loader_Autoloader::getInstance()->registerNamespace('Zend_');\r\n\r\nclass TrickyAdapter extends Zend_Translate_Adapter_Array {\r\n    public function translate($messageId, $locale = null) {\r\n        return parent::translate($messageId, $locale) . '[XY]';\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nZend_Registry::set(\r\n    'Zend_Translate',\r\n    new Zend_Translate('TrickyAdapter', array('en' => array()))\r\n);\r\n\r\nfunction simple_form() {\r\n    return new Zend_Form(\r\n        array(\r\n            'method' => 'post',\r\n            \r\n            'elements' => array(\r\n                'title' => array(\r\n                    'type' => 'text',\r\n                    \r\n                    'options' => array(\r\n                        'label' => 'Bug title',\r\n                    )\r\n                ),\r\n                \r\n                'submit' => array(\r\n                    'type' => 'button',\r\n                    'options' => array(\r\n                        'label' => 'Send',\r\n                        'type' => 'submit',\r\n                    )\r\n                ),\r\n            )\r\n        )\r\n    );\r\n}\r\n\r\necho \"\\n\" . simple_form()->render(new Zend_View()) . \"\\n\\n\";\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nUnder ZF 1.9.7 the code above outputs:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n<form enctype=\"application\/x-www-form-urlencoded\" method=\"post\" action=\"\"><dl class=\"zend_form\">\r\n<dt id=\"title-label\"><label for=\"title\" class=\"optional\">Bug title[XY]<\/label><\/dt>\r\n<dd id=\"title-element\">\r\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"title\" id=\"title\" value=\"\"><\/dd>\r\n<dt id=\"submit-label\">&nbsp;<\/dt><dd id=\"submit-element\">\r\n<button name=\"submit\" id=\"submit\" type=\"submit\">Send[XY]<\/button><\/dd><\/dl><\/form>\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nWhile under ZF 1.10.0 and 1.10.1 it's:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n<form enctype=\"application\/x-www-form-urlencoded\" method=\"post\" action=\"\"><dl class=\"zend_form\">\r\n<dt id=\"title-label\"><label for=\"title\" class=\"optional\">Bug title[XY][XY]<\/label><\/dt>\r\n<dd id=\"title-element\">\r\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"title\" id=\"title\" value=\"\"><\/dd>\r\n<dt id=\"submit-label\">&nbsp;<\/dt><dd id=\"submit-element\">\r\n<button name=\"submit\" id=\"submit\" type=\"submit\">Send[XY][XY]<\/button><\/dd><\/dl><\/form>\r\n{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ikr",
                        "name": "ikr",
                        "displayName": "Ivan Krechetov",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-02-17T07:08:44.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-02-17T07:08:44.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41922",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jokke",
                        "name": "jokke",
                        "displayName": "Joakim Nyg\u00e5rd",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The question is whether the translation should be restricted to the element's or the Label decorator's getLabel() method. I think it makes the most sense to place the translation in the decorator - as close to the user as possible, but I am not sure if this change will break anything depending on the element doing the translation.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jokke",
                        "name": "jokke",
                        "displayName": "Joakim Nyg\u00e5rd",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-08-09T06:51:21.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-08-09T06:51:21.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/43823",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=tomas.fejfar@gmail.com",
                        "name": "tomas.fejfar@gmail.com",
                        "displayName": "Tom\u00e1\u0161 Fejfar",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The only legitimate place to translate the value is where the value is received - i.e. in element's getLabel() method. Decorator's purpose is to receive some value and wrap it around the current content. Not tu modify it in any way. ",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=tomas.fejfar@gmail.com",
                        "name": "tomas.fejfar@gmail.com",
                        "displayName": "Tom\u00e1\u0161 Fejfar",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-12-27T04:05:18.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-12-27T04:05:18.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/44288",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=nicolaedima",
                        "name": "nicolaedima",
                        "displayName": "Nicolae Dima",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "This can be fixed fast, by commenting these lines\r\n\r\n- Zend_Form_Element_Submit - Line 80 to 83 <-- These most be also commented since you already call the parent method get label, which will result in a double translation from Zend_Form_Element\r\n- Zend_Form_Decorator_Label - Line 260 to 263 <-- Decorator should not be used for translation, it is out of purpose",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=nicolaedima",
                        "name": "nicolaedima",
                        "displayName": "Nicolae Dima",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-02-06T07:12:36.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-02-06T07:12:36.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/46861",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hschletz",
                        "name": "hschletz",
                        "displayName": "Holger Schletz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "OK, it's bug hunt days again. Time to bump this issue. Any chance to see it fixed this time? It's been around for ages, as well as the proposed simple fix, like in the previous comment.\r\n\r\nBTW, the issue with Zend_Form_Element_Submit has been silently fixed in the meantime, but it still occurs with Zend_Form_Decorator_Label.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hschletz",
                        "name": "hschletz",
                        "displayName": "Holger Schletz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-05-28T08:27:05.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-05-28T08:27:05.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/46862",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=kblomqvist",
                        "name": "kblomqvist",
                        "displayName": "Kim Blomqvist",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Patch attached. Holger - where did you check that the issue with {{Zend_Form_Element_Submit}} has been already fixed. It wasn't in my trunk.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=kblomqvist",
                        "name": "kblomqvist",
                        "displayName": "Kim Blomqvist",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-05-28T08:50:25.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-05-28T08:50:25.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/46864",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hschletz",
                        "name": "hschletz",
                        "displayName": "Holger Schletz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "It has not been fixed in Zend_Form_Element_Submit itself - in fact, removing the translate() call there would result in an untranslated label. Something else in the code path has changed so that now only Zend_Form_Decorator_Label is still affected.\r\n\r\nI don't know where this change has been made and whether the new behavior is intentional or just happened to stop the bug from occurring. The facts are: with the current implementation, the label gets translated once for Zend_Form_Element_Submit::getLabel() (correct) and twice for Zend_Form_Decorator_Label::getLabel() (incorrect). This might need more investigation, but removing the translate() call from Zend_Form_Decorator_Label::getLabel() would at least be an interim solution that actually works. It could easily be reverted if it turns out to be the wrong place for the fix.\r\n\r\nThe fix has been proposed and known to work flawlessly by several users for a long time, so I think it would be safe to provide it as a working solution. There are already discussions about restructuring and where translations should actually be done, but that's more of a long term goal.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hschletz",
                        "name": "hschletz",
                        "displayName": "Holger Schletz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-05-28T09:36:19.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-05-28T09:36:19.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/48411",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hschletz",
                        "name": "hschletz",
                        "displayName": "Holger Schletz",
                        "active": true
                    },
